name: myBase Database File
summary: Learn about .NYF files and view a list of programs that open them.

windows.name: Open over 400 file formats with File Viewer Plus.Free Download

content: Data entered into a myBase database is saved in a tree-structured outline format. The files are also compressed using zlib compression to reduce their file size.

description: An NYF file is a data file saved by myBase, a free-form database system. It may contain unstructured text, formatted documents, images, webpages, emails, and other files.
